Path: Basic Types
Content:
The following pages contain detail on the basic types available in Nushell.
Variables, parameters, input values, and return values can be annotated with these types.
Internal Implementation: See 
``enum Value``
 in 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/blob/main/crates/nu-protocol/src/value/mod.rs] ``nushell/crates/nu-protocol/src/value/mod.rs``
.
